new_pokemon.name: Venusaur
new_pokemon.description: The plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.

new_pokemon.name: Charmeleon
new_pokemon.description: When it swings its burning tail, it elevates the temperature to unbearably high levels.

new_pokemon.name: Charizard
new_pokemon.description: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. Known to cause forest fires unintentionally.

new_pokemon.name: Wartortle
new_pokemon.description: Often hides in water to stalk unwary prey. For swimming fast, it moves its ears to maintain balance.

new_pokemon.name: Blastoise
new_pokemon.description: A brutal Pok√©mon with pressurized water jets on its shell. They are used for high speed tackles.

new_pokemon.name: Nidoqueen
new_pokemon.description: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.

new_pokemon.name: Clefairy
new_pokemon.description: Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers. It is rare and found only in certain areas.

new_pokemon.name: Nidoking
new_pokemon.description: It uses its powerful tail in battle to smash, constrict, then break the prey's bones.

new_pokemon.name: Alakazam
new_pokemon.description: Its brain can outperform a super-computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

new_pokemon.name: Tentacruel
new_pokemon.description: The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey.
